name: Plague of Ashitaka - Taking Lives on Ancient Tides
description:
The boys in Plague of Ashitaka gave me a whole load of their EP, 'Taking Lives on Ancient Tides' from when I put on a gig for them. So I decided to sell a few on here for £3 only! There's 20 on here, perhaps more will go on depending on how well these sell.

Everything thats sold on here, and all the money from it goes straight to the POA boys, so you're helping a good cause! As soon as I start selling, all proceeds go to the band and not in my pocket.
